-- Hachette, HarperCollins, Simon & Schuster Settle E-Book Case
-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 2012-04-11T16:20:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-11/hachette-harpercollins-simon-schuster-settle-e-book-case.html
Hachette Book Group (USA),
HarperCollins Publishers LLC and Simon & Schuster Inc. agreed to
settle an antitrust case over the pricing of e-books, the U.S.
Justice Department said in a statement.  The case against  Apple Inc. (AAPL) ,Holtzbrinck Publishers LLC and
Penguin Group (USA) continues, the department said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vivek Shankar at 
 vshankar3@bloomberg.net  